# Fix Container Launch & Error Status -1

## Status: ✅ All Fixes Applied, Build Successful

## Root Causes Identified & Fixed

### 1. **Fatal: Bionic LD_PRELOAD Using Relative Paths** (Primary Cause)
**Files**: [BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java)

Bionic mode runs natively on the device (no proot). The dynamic linker **cannot** find libraries by relative name alone — it needs full absolute paths. Our `LD_PRELOAD` was set to:
```
libandroid-sysvshm.so:libevshim.so:libredirect-bionic.so
```
But the upstream (working) version uses:
```
/data/data/.../imagefs/usr/lib/libandroid-sysvshm.so:/data/data/.../imagefs/usr/lib/libevshim.so:...
```

When the linker can't find `LD_PRELOAD` libraries, the process immediately terminates with exit code -1.

**Fix**: Restored absolute paths (`sysvPath`, `evshimPath`, `replacePath`) for `LD_PRELOAD` in both [execGuestProgram()](file:///tmp/GameNative-upstream/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/GlibcProgramLauncherComponent.java#172-223) and [execShellCommand()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/xserver/XServerScreen.kt#2048-2051).

### 2. **Fatal: Null Pointer Exception in BionicProgramLauncherComponent** 
**Files**: [BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java)

Three places called `wineInfo.isArm64EC()` without null checks, causing NPE → exit code -1:

| Location | Before | After |
|---|---|---|
| [start()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java#102-138) L105 | `wineInfo.isArm64EC()` | `wineInfo != null && wineInfo.isArm64EC()` |
| [execGuestProgram()](file:///tmp/GameNative-upstream/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/GlibcProgramLauncherComponent.java#172-223) L315 | `!wineInfo.isArm64EC()` | `wineInfo == null \|\| !wineInfo.isArm64EC()` |
| [getFinalCommand()](file:///tmp/GameNative-upstream/app/src/main/java/com/winlator/xenvironment/components/BionicProgramLauncherComponent.java#351-365) L475 | `wineInfo.isArm64EC()` | `wineInfo != null && wineInfo.isArm64EC()` |

### 3. **Stuck on "Launching game..." for Container Opens**
**Files**: [PluviaMain.kt](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/PluviaMain.kt)

The `bootToContainer` parameter was missing from [preLaunchApp()](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/PluviaMain.kt#1048-1378). When the user clicked "Open Container", the function proceeded to Steam cloud sync which could hang indefinitely.

**Fix**: Added `bootToContainer: Boolean = false` parameter. When `true`, cloud sync is skipped and the container boots directly to the desktop. Updated all callers:
- `onClickPlay` → passes `bootToContainer = asContainer`
- [onTestGraphics](file:///home/max/Build/GameNative-Performance/GameNative-Performance/app/src/main/java/app/gamenative/ui/screen/library/appscreen/BaseAppScreen.kt#378-385) → passes `bootToContainer = true`
- Retry path → propagates `bootToContainer`

### 4. **Wrong TMPDIR for Bionic**
The Bionic TMPDIR was set to `/tmp` instead of `/usr/tmp` (the upstream value).

**Fix**: Changed to `rootDir.getPath() + "/usr/tmp"`.

